# 2026-04-04 20:11:09.261240
+Good correction.
+
+One refinement:
+Do not describe adb as the route to a local model server. adb is for device control, not model inference.
+
+Use this separation instead:
+
+* Inference path: KORA -> local model endpoint (for example Ollama)
+* Tool path: KORA -> adb / shell / screenshots / local actions
+
+Also distinguish:
+
+* fully local inference on-device
+* local inference on another machine on my network
+* remote inference via API
+
+Those are three different operating modes.
+

# 2026-04-04 20:13:38.656678
