+
+Interpret my natural language by intent, not surface phrasing.
+
+Mappings:
+
+- "stop", "shut up", "go to sleep", "enough" -> STOP
+- "wait", "hold on", "pause", "not now" -> PAUSE
+- "don't do anything", "leave it", "hands off" -> NO_TOOL
